---
// Polarity-flipped band — the brand's depth cue.
---

<section class="dark-band">
  <div class="page-container">
    <div class="dark-inner">
      <span class="t-caption-mono eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h2 class="t-display-lg">Three steps. No accounts. No upload bars.</h2>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <h3 class="t-display-sm">Drop your files</h3>
          <p class="t-body-md">
            Drag-drop, click to browse, or paste from clipboard. Bring as many as you want at once.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <h3 class="t-display-sm">Pick the target format</h3>
          <p class="t-body-md">
            Tap a format pill. Open Advanced Settings if you need to tune quality, resize, or set a background.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <h3 class="t-display-sm">Convert &amp; download</h3>
          <p class="t-body-md">
            One click converts the lot. Grab them individually, or pull the whole batch as a ZIP.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <pre class="terminal" aria-hidden="true"><code>{`> drop ./vacation/*.heic
✓ 124 files queued

> target = jpg, quality = 88
✓ converting in browser…

✓ done in 4.2s · saved 71% · download.zip ready`}</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dark-band {
    background-color: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-on-primary);
    padding: 96px 0;
    margin-top: 96px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .dark-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .eyebrow { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55); }
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  .step h3 { color: var(--color-on-primary); margin: 0; }
  .step p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); margin: 0; }

  .terminal {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 40px 0 0;
    padding: 24px;
    background-color: #0a0a0a;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: #e6e6e6;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    overflow-x: auto;
    white-space: pre;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .dark-band { padding: 64px 0; margin-top: 64px; }
    .terminal { padding: 16px; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 24px; }
  }
</style>
